  "customHelp": "Experimental host setup: one player can select FS Auto Setup Host, then Start. The game will try to spread Loot/Treasure/Monster/Room/Bonus Soul cards into the shared zones automatically. Character assignment is still manual from FS Character Pool and FS Starting Items Pool.",
